Positive Feedback.content:
My guess is that the 4th one is the real one.
It feels like a great opening scene of the movie and do not forget that FNaF 2 is supposed to be a prequel to the original game. So having Abby, Vanessa & Mike so early in the movie. Doesn't really make that much sense. And the mystery part of the 4th script definitely feels best, because it sets up so many questions that will or won't be solved in the rest of the movie.

And do not forget that it might have been a misremembered memory from a kid stuck inside of the withered animatronic suits. Memory can be extremely unreliable and easily manipulated. As we have seen in the first movie. So do not forget that the kids and the father could actually be totally different people. ^^;
